//==============================================================================
//  HEMT Extrinsic Resistances and Bias-Independent Overlap Capacitances
//  Part of GaN HEMT Compact Model Library
//
//  Version      : v1.0.0
//  Release Date : 2026-06-19
//
//  Description:
//      This section models extrinsic source/drain/gate resistances and
//      bias-independent overlap capacitances for GaN HEMT devices.
//      Includes geometry scaling, temperature dependence, and first-order
//      resistance correction effects.
//
//  Developed by:
//
//  * Sahra Ebrahimmagham (Researcher, AUT)
//  * Dr. Majid Shalchian (Assistant Professor, AUT)
//  * Dr. Farzan Jazaeri (Researcher, EPFL)
